properties.headline: Special Weather Statement issued January 7 at 10:59AM MST by NWS Cheyenne WY
properties.description:
Although the High Wind Warning will expire on time this morning,
winds may gust between 50 to 55 MPH over the next few hours along
Interstate 25 between the Colorado border and Glendo, and along
Interstate 80 from Cheyenne to Laramie.

Please use caution if driving as strong crosswinds can cause blow
overs and accidents. These winds are expected to slowly subside
this afternoon into tonight, but may increase again on Wednesday.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING WILL EXPIRE AT 11 AM BUT WINDS WILL GUST BETWEEN 50 TO 55 MPH THROUGH EARLY THIS AFTERNOON
